k. heteroaromatic rings can be additionally substituted with acylamino, alkanoyl, alkoxy, alkoxycarbonyl, alkoxycarbonylalkyl, alkyl, alkylamino, alkylsulfonyl, alkylthio, amino, arylsulfonyl, aryl sulfonyl, benzoyl, carboxy, cyano, dialkylamino, halo, fluoralkyl, hydroxy, mercapto, nitro, phenyl, phenoxy, pyrrolidin-1-yl, piperidin-1-yl, 4-arylpiperidin-1-yl, morpholin-4-yl, 4-arylpiperazin-1-yl, sulfamoyl, fluoromethyl, difluoromethyl, or trifluoromethyl; 
